ts to our FP\nmodel necessary to make this formalism a practical companion to shear analyses\nin weak lensing surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 16:50:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 23:29:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-10"}
