n intermediate\nstep, our map applies directly between gauge invariant quantities. Our findings\nprovide a starting point for an alternative approach to the binary problem. We\nconclude with future directions and some speculations on the classical double\ncopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 18:54:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 18:08:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2019 19:03:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2020 18:27:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-03"}
