erved. The excellent scaling of area with $Pe_{\\lambda}^{1/2}$\noccurs even though the probability density function (p.d.f.) of the scalar\ngradient is very close to exponential for $Re_{\\lambda}=98$ but approximately\nlognormal when $Re_{\\lambda}=633$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 22:27:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
