thod for graphical model estimation is assessed through simulation and\nanalysis of functional brain connectivity during a motor task.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 23:42:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2019 18:58:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 11 Oct 2020 03:16:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 22:56:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-04"}
