V2. The experimental results show our module is more\nefficient while performing favorably against its counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 01:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 08:26:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Mar 2020 00:58:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 13:53:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
