' assessments: only the results for some tags are in agreement with\nthe expectations. Thus, we propose - based on our results - the use of novelty\nscore U for measuring novelty quantitatively, but question the use of novelty\nscore W.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 06:41:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
